<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Services</title>
  <style>
    body {
        background-image: url("img/servicesbackground.jpeg");
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #555555;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .service {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .service img {
      max-width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .service .service-details {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .service h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #555555;
    }

    .service p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #777777;
    }

    .go-back-link {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #060606;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .go-back-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }


    .footer {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #777777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Services</h2>

    <div class="service">
      <img src="/img/services1.jpg" alt="Service 1">
      <div class="service-details">
        <h3>Web Design</h3>
        <p>Our web design services involve creating beautifully crafted websites that are visually appealing and user-friendly. We specialize in creating unique designs that reflect your brand and captivate your audience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service">
      <img src="/img/services2.jpg" alt="Service 2">
      <div class="service-details">
        <h3>Mobile App Development</h3>
        <p>With our mobile app development services, we can bring your app ideas to life. Our experienced team will work closely with you to design and develop a stunning and functional mobile app that meets your specific requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  <a href="/" class="go-back-link">Go Back</a>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2023 Your Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>